        "replaceString": "```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>状态栏</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <style>\n        /* 根容器 */\n        .status-bar-wrapper {\n            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 500px;\n            margin: 1em auto;\n            user-select: none;\n            -webkit-user-select: none;\n        }\n\n        /* details/summary 折叠效果 */\n        .status-bar-wrapper details {\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            background: #fdf6f7;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(213, 186, 191, 0.3);\n            border: 1px solid #fbeaed;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        .status-bar-wrapper details[open] {\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(213, 186, 191, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .status-bar-wrapper summary {\n            position: relative; /* [新增] 为绝对定位的子元素提供基准 */\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            list-style: none;\n            outline: none;\n        }\n        .status-bar-wrapper summary::-webkit-details-marker {\n            display: none;\n        }\n\n        .status-bar-wrapper .summary-title {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 10px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #d58a99;\n        }\n\n        /* [新增] “哥哥在看着你呢” 这行小字的样式 */\n        .status-bar-wrapper .secret-message {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 13px; /* 微调垂直位置 */\n            left: 125px; /* 微调水平位置，使其紧跟在“当前状态”后面 */\n            font-size: 0.65em; /* 非常小的字号 */\n            font-weight: normal;\n            color: #e6aab6; /* 一种更柔和的粉色